channel.title: Just a warning
channel.description:
Dont send any code you want dont public to pplsuqbawlz or Speljohan. Runeown got control of Speljohan accts a while back. But it has just been recently found that he has control of pplsuqbawlz's accts. It would be helpful if a admin here posted the ips on pplsuqbawlz forum acct. A announcement i made at my site:
Here are the reasons. 1. Runeown has taken control of pplsuqbawlz's msn and forum accts. We do not know how. For all we know pplsuqbawlz might be runeown. We are working with many head staffs of other forums to piece this together. 2. Zymic which is probably anouther alias of runeown may have had at one time or anouther over the course of the last year had access to the following forum databases: Tainted-Ones, fagex. 3. We know for fact he had access to the kyab database and new/old runeown.net which has thousands of members. I think this is just the tip of the iceberg. Their could be many more forum databases and sites he may have access to. We also know for a fact that he has taken items from members in this community by phising user/password from a script he posted on this site.
